FT  24 APR 91 / UK Company News: Conder sale set to raise Pounds 23m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Conder Group is to raise a maximum of Pounds 23m from the sale of 61 per
cent of Conder Products, which supplies petrol forecourt canopies.
Conder Group will receive an initial Pounds 15m plus a performance related
Pounds 8m.
CIN Venture Managers will hold 56 per cent and the mangers will hold the
other 5 per cent.
