FT  23 APR 91 / International Company News: Fred Carr - Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In early editions of the Financial Times of April 13 a picture of Mr Fred
Carr, the chief executive of WI Carr (Investments) was published. The
picture should have been of Mr Fred Carr, the chairman of First Executive.
